Package org.electrocodeogram.module

Class Summary
Module This abstract class represents an ECG analysis module.
ModuleClassLoader The ModuleClassLoader is able to load classes directly from a given location in the file system, which should be the module directory.
ModuleDescriptor  
ModuleRegistry This is the central ModuleRegistry which maintains information about all currently instanciated modules and all module class files in the module directory from which module instances could be created at runtime.
TestModule This is a simple test module. every event that is received is immediatly send.
